I removed this sentence because I believe it is false: "The seven Narakas are: Atala, Vitala, Sutala, Talatala, Mahatala, Rasatala, Patala." These 7 regions are specifically termed the 7 Patalas and are part of the 14 Lokas in Vedic cosmology.
